      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Samoset%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The first school in Samoset opened in October 1926, starting with just 30 children housed in the community hall.",
